verbose_text: Stockmann-Juvala et al and Chaudhari et al demonstrated that fumonisin B1 and the trichothecene, T-2 toxin, elicited apoptotic cell death as a consequence of increased ROS production and reduced glutathione levels in cervical cancer and glioblastomas, respectively.
evidence: fumonisin B1 and the trichothecene, T-2 toxin, elicited apoptotic cell death
